-- Shuaa Capital Private Equity Unit Agrees to Sell 22% Stake in Rotana Hotel
-- Shaji Mathew
-- 2010-07-01T05:24:06Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-01/shuaa-capital-private-equity-unit-agrees-to-sell-22-stake-in-rotana-hotel.html

          
          
             Shuaa Partners, the private equity
unit of Shuaa Capital PSC, agreed to sell a 22 percent stake in
Rotana Hotel Management Corp.  
 The offer to purchase the shares owned by Shuaa Partners
Fund 1 was made by a shareholder in Rotana Hotel, the company
said in a statement to Dubai bourse today. The transaction is
due to be completed in a few weeks after approval from the Abu
Dhabi Department of Economic Development, it said.  
          
          


  


        